message:
{{#is_alert}}
The storage process has very high durability lag - that is, the time it takes for data fetched by the storage server to be written to disk.
{{/is_alert}}
{{#is_warning}}
The storage process has higher than usual durability lag - that is, the time it takes for data fetched by the storage server to be written to disk.
{{/is_warning}}

This may indicate that the database cluster cannot keep up with the workload. Sometimes, storage servers can also struggle if faced with a huge number of reads of the keys they store, preventing progress on writes.
